data.description: Experience the pinnacle of luxury living in Gainesville with this remarkable dream home! Prepare to be mesmerized by the breathtaking waterfront view that greets you as you step onto the exquisitely designed front-facing deck. The allure doesn't end there – step inside to discover an interior that exudes elegance and sophistication, with a master suite conveniently located on the main level.    This residence offers endless possibilities for a single-family yearning to establish roots in a vibrant and picturesque community. Nestled in an area renowned for its beauty and charm, this property is ideally situated to embrace the idyllic lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Plus, the highly acclaimed North Forsyth High School ensures an exceptional educational experience for families seeking top-tier schooling for their children.    Welcome home to a world of unparalleled beauty, comfort, and opportunity. Embrace the enchantment of Gainesville and seize the chance to make this exquisite property your own. Don't miss out on this extraordinary chance to create lasting memories in a place where your dreams can truly flourish.
